4.title: What is DynAPI
4.content: DynAPI is a completely dynamic Rest-API for PostgreSQL Databases. It offers realtime-adjusted endpoints and a generated documentation with Redoc and Swagger . It offers great customization over the configuration file, the plugin system or the pre-build plugins .
